Machiavelli and Gerrard are just one of the many names the new professor of Ceoren Academy uses to disguise his identity, and now he can add one more to his list, Professor Ludger Cherish. The real Ludger Cherish dies on board a train during a terrorist attack, making him the perfect target for a new identity. Little does the new professor know, Ludger Cherish was involved in something deep and secret. The new Professor Ludger has to be careful to not get caught by the school and the dangerous secret society.
(Source: WEBTOONS)

One day the strongest person in the world disappeared. An old man who was suffering from dementia and couldnt remember himself appeared in front of the village boy So-Woon. So-Woon takes care of him carefully and later the old man teaches him martial arts. One day he finds that the old man whom he was taking care of and who taught him martial arts disappeared. So-Woon knew that the old man must have come to his senses and left him without saying anything. Six years later So-Woon becomes the symbol of Pungcheon.
